[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | 9 | LOW | Security | Architecture diagram, API Gateway | No authentication mechanism discussed for the dispatch API endpoint. Unauthenticated endpoint could allow spoofed dispatch requests. | Add mTLS or IAM SigV4 auth for CAD integration, rate limiting, schema validation. |
